 2495: 101: ## Data Flow
 2496: 102: 
 2497: 103: ### Synchronization Flow
 2498: 104: 
 2499: 105: ```mermaid
 2500: 106: sequenceDiagram
 2501: 107:     participant T as Trigger
 2502: 108:     participant S as Sync Service
 2503: 109:     participant E as External API
