21188: 18537: 133: ## Rate Limiting
21189: 18538: 134: 
21190: 18539: 135: ### How does rate limiting work?
21191: 18540: 136: 
21192: 18541: 137: ```typescript
21193: 18542: 138: const rateLimiter = {
21194: 18543: 139:   tokens: 100,
21195: 18544: 140:   refillRate: 10,
