21231: 18580: 176: ### How does the cache hierarchy work?
21232: 18581: 177: 
21233: 18582: 178: 1. Memory cache (L1)
21234: 18583: 179: 2. LRU cache (L2)
21235: 18584: 180: 3. Firestore (persistent)
