25313: 22662:  62: 
25314: 22663:  63: ### Format Verification
25315: 22664:  64: 
25316: 22665:  65: ```typescript
25317: 22666:  66: export async function isValidFormat(
25318: 22667:  67:   buffer: Buffer
25319: 22668:  68: ): Promise<boolean> {
25320: 22669:  69:   try {
