30285: 210: ## Error Monitoring
30286: 211: 
30287: 212: ### Error Aggregation
30288: 213: 
30289: 214: ```typescript
30290: 215: interface ErrorAggregate {
30291: 216:   count: number;
30292: 217:   lastOccurrence: Date;
30293: 218:   contexts: string[];
30294: 219: }
