30905:  16: ## Configuration
30906:  17: 
30907:  18: ### Size Limits
30908:  19: 
30909:  20: ```typescript
30910:  21: export const IMAGE_LIMITS = {
30911:  22:   MAX_SIZE: 10 * 1024 * 1024,  // 10MB
