170:      cardsProcessed: 50,
171:      updatedCount: 10,
172:      duration: "5m30s",
173:      timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
174:    });
175:    ```
176: 
177: 2. **Error Context**:
178: 
179:    ```typescript
